name: Freshbooksdotnet
body:
### Welcome to FreshbooksDotNet

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.

### Universal
We've created a set of classes compatibles with the API of Freshbooks for making your integration more easy.

### Mono or .net
It doesn't matter our code is compatible with both

### What you can do

Create, Delete, Query Invoices with your account in freshbooks.com with c# classes ready for you.


### Authors and Contributors
